cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper proposes an automated vision-based score estimation model for action quality assessment. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed model uses deep metric learning and score estimation modules, which are AI techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of regression-based solutions and proposes a new scoring system that uses deep metric learning. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with action videos and proposes a scoring model for Olympics Diving and Gymnastic vaults. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper discusses the issue of judgment bias and proposes an alternate opinion using automated vision-based score estimation models.
